Title: Grimtusk's Sister
Description:
Last is my sister, Naluki. She helps run the inn at Iskaara now.

Just give her this letter. 

Don't open it.
ObjectivesText: Deliver Grimtusk's letter to his sister, Naluki, in Iskaara.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver Grimtusk's letter to his sister Naluki in Iskaara.
RewardText:
Why, well aren't you just a fresh fish hopping out of the water! 

What's this? A letter from Grimtusk?
